gov.usgs.anss.query

Class Run

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.query.Run
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Run>

    public class Run
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Run>
    This class creates a list of contiguous blocks. A block can be added to it and will be rejected if it is not contiguous at the end. The user just attempts to add the next data block in time to each of the known runs, and creates a new run with the block when none of the existing ones accepts it.
